QuestData.Title: Meet with Avaros Dawnglaive
QuestData.Description: You should make your way to Orgrimmar as soon as you can, $n. Avaros Dawnglaive has sent word that he wishes to speak with you about a matter of importance to the Horde. Look for him at The Barracks in the Valley of Honor.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Avaros Dawnglaive at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Avaros Dawnglaive at The Barracks in Orgrimmar
